{
 "name": "RPlog_Severed_Connections",
 "title": "Severed Connections",
 "summary": "While sorting through the dusty old house of her late mentor on a quiet day, the Jedi Jessalyn shares an easy, tender moment with Luke Skywalker, unearthing a bottle of ancient Alderaani wine and offering to drink it with him. The serenity shatters when the death of Orson Tighe -- struck down by the Jedi-killer Simon Sezirok -- crashes through the Force, hitting Luke with such ferocity that he is overwhelmed by raw grief and fury, shattering the bottle and raging aloud at his fallen friend in a rare descent into darkness. Jessalyn collapses on the broken glass, sobbing for Orson and tormented by guilt that she was not there to help him against Sezirok. Frightened by the depth of Luke's anger yet anchored to the Light, she watches him slowly master his rage and shut the door on his wounded soul as the two grieving Jedi kneel together amid the spilled wine.",
